create table "C_MapMarker"
(
MARKERID NUMBER(32) not null,
MALLID NUMBER(32)),
BUILDINGID NUMBER(32),
FLOORID NUMBER(32),
MARKERTYPE INTEGER,
MARKERNAME VARCHAR2(200),
PICHEIGHT DECIMAL(10,2),
PICWIDTH DECIMAL(10,2),
PICANGEL DECIMAL(10,2),
VECTORYINFO VARCHAR2(4000),
ENABLE INTEGER,
STARTTIME TIMESTAMP,
ENDTIME TIMESTAMP,
CREATEBY NUMBER(32),
CREATETIME TIMESTAMP,
MODIFYBY NUMBER(32),
MODIFYTIME TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_C_MAPMARKER primary key (MARKERID)
);
